{
  "stem": "18670.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 297.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I arrived in New York on Washington's birthday, February 22.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My grandfather.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Since 1904, my mother's father.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was an Orthodox Jew who prepared children for the bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He belonged to a real shul.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He lived on 102nd Street between Second Avenue and First Avenue, Manhattan.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a real Orthodox, old-fashioned religious Jew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Little man.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And actually, the people that we got-- that really got the papers for us and so on wasn't he.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was his granddaughter and his daughter-in-law that were pushing and pushing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the papers were made out-- because he was not wealthy, were made out by the president of the shul, who was a wholesale butter and egg dealer on Second Avenue.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's how we came here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no kashrut there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the day I left Vienna, with the exception of the time that I tried to get into the temple on Yom Kippur, I never entered another temple 'til I came to the United States.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't have an opportunity.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't have my mind set on that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, the two experiences I had in Brussel, one I have no food for goyims, and the other experience I had, you gotta a ticket, turned me off.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I lived with him for a short while.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- when I arrived at-- in Hoboken, the ship, Dutch boat February 22nd, my grandfather greeted us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He came down.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had to get you out of the-- out of Hoboken, out of the port.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he came down with a cousin, the one that helped us to come here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She's actually only a half-cousin, because it's a half-brother of my mother's.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But she came down with him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he greeted us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The greeting was in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
